data.description: A must see!!! This spacious one-story home located in Deltona features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a 2-car garage; large landscaped front yard and backyard. Well located near K-12 schools, middle and elementary schools, library, city hall, Daytona State College campus and I-4. This is a home that has been lovingly cared for since its construction. New roof 2018, NEW A/C 2020 and clean A/C Air Ducts 2022... Also well maintained exterior. Covered porch and fenced throughout. NEW 2022 Luxury tile throughout the house, Renovated ceiling including LED LIGHT & PAINT 2022. Deltona is the perfect community to call home, close to schools, commerce and recreation. It is conveniently located just 5 minutes from I-4 and close to restaurants, hospitals, shopping and all the world class entertainment Central Florida has to offer and just 30 minutes from the beach. This beautiful home won't last long, so call and book your private showing today.
